1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses a handover algorithm for LTE networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper proposes a new algorithm to optimize system performance, which involves information theory concepts. 
3. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking) - The paper deals with improving the handover mechanism in LTE networks, which is a communication and networking problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper evaluates the performance of the proposed algorithm in terms of system throughput, which is a key metric for multimedia applications. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new handover algorithm, which involves designing and implementing an efficient algorithm for minimizing handovers and system delay.
